---
import PageLayout from "@/layouts/PageLayout.astro";
---

<PageLayout
  title="About | Erika & the Wolf"
  description="Erika & the Wolf — a musical storytime for children featuring woodwind quintet and live narration."
  heading="Erika & the Wolf"
>
  <div class="about-content">

    <p class="about-tagline">A Musical Storytime for Children</p>

    <div class="about-video">
      <iframe
        src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Vo-iAtPyuSg"
        title="Erika & the Wolf performance at Lake City Library, Seattle WA, September 21 2025"
        frameborder="0"
        allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
        allowfullscreen
      ></iframe>
      <p class="video-caption">September 21, 2025 — Lake City Library, Seattle, WA</p>
    </div>

    <div class="about-body">
      <p>Erika and the Wolf features our refreshed version of the classic tale Peter and the Wolf, featuring flute, oboe, clarinet, bassoon, and French horn, along with live narration. We also perform selections from Aesop's Fables, and have audience interaction pieces including the Clapping Song, Pink Panther Theme (children snap or clap along with the music), along with our ever popular Q&A.</p>

      <p>We are all professional musicians and teachers and enjoy presenting music and storytime performances specifically for children.</p>
    </div>

  </div>
</PageLayout>